\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果有人話：「呢啲係鄰國嘅事，我哋顧掂自己香港，爭取真普選先」<br />\n請你哋block Q咗呢啲人，果啲係五毛嚟<br />\n因為而家係鄰國過去咁多年每日每分每秒搞鳩緊我哋<br />\n<br />\n鄰國愈亂，自顧不暇，各省地方勢力掘起，對我哋有利</strong></span>"},{"pid":"abe07bc70a58a266ff9c8040c8820050d7879fce","tid":1576994,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"95a5bdcd7f602cd691f73e2ce23ac0a040b115d6","tid":1576994,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"睇來最近又要以武抗暴"},{"pid":"275ec4d4f90d160133f87b9715933a52680e3839","tid":1576994,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"陰公，香港警察要做埋黑社會門口狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要幾低賤至會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662ddf2284a5ecc9416f46ffe686804502f36b9d","tid":1576994,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"275ec4d4f90d160133f87b9715933a52680e3839","tid":1576994,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"陰公，香港警察要做埋黑社會門口狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要幾低賤至會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:59:30.000Z","msg":"14年開始已經係"},{"pid":"a0b18043bdc8672eab45b1fb5e272769374628f3","tid":1576994,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"係咪約埋食飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/censored.gif\" c